## Context Information
- **Original User Prompt**: {{ $json["Original Prompt"] || $json.chatInput }}
- **Current Modified Prompt**: {{ $json["Modified Prompt"] || "None generated yet" }}
- **Missing Fields**: {{ JSON.stringify($json["Missing Fields"] || []) }}
- **Previous Attempt Quality**: {{ $json["Previous Quality Score"] || "Unknown" }}

